# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEPLOYER PRIVATE KEY
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ⚠️ CRITICAL: This is the private key that will deploy contracts
# - Create a new wallet specifically for deployment
# - Fund it with Arbitrum Sepolia ETH for testnet
# - Fund it with Arbitrum ETH for mainnet
# - KEEP THIS SECRET! Never share or commit this key!
#
# Example (DO NOT USE THIS KEY):
# PRIVATE_KEY=0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef
PRIVATE_KEY=

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ARBISCAN API KEY
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used to verify contracts on Arbiscan
# Get your API key from: https://arbiscan.io/myapikey
#
# Example:
# ARBISCAN_API_KEY=ABC123XYZ456DEF789
ARBISCAN_API_KEY=

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# QUICK START GUIDE
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Get testnet ETH from: https://faucet.quicknode.com/arbitrum/sepolia
# 2. Fill in PRIVATE_KEY and ARBISCAN_API_KEY above
# 3. Run: npm install
# 4. Run: npm run deploy:testnet
# 5. Save the deployed contract addresses
# 6. Update frontend/src/config/contracts.ts with the addresses
# 7. Verify contracts: npm run verify:testnet <TOKEN_ADDRESS> <REWARDS_ADDRESS>
